Trinity::

She put on the brakes, but skid into Aerotaur's leg. She rubbed her 
little pink nose and gave a slight growl at him. She walked up to the 
new bot. "Yeah, you can join us. We can always use another bot to 
play tag with." she said with a slight giggle.

> ::Aerotaur::
>       "Hold on fair lady."  He runs after Trinity launching himself 
over her 
> and landing in front facing the new bot.  "Who are you?  You are 
welcome to 
> join us in our travels, as long as you don't try to harm us."
